---

<section
  class="w-full min-h-[550px] h-screen bg-cover bg-center flex items-center px-[4%] pb-[150px] pt-[100px] sm:pt-0"
  style="background-image: url('/img/lakesbg44.png')"
>
  <div class="hero-content w-full md:w-7/12 md:ml-auto max-w-[600px] mx-auto md:mx-0 p-5">
    <h1 class="hero-heading text-5xl leading-tight mb-3">
      Empowering <span class="hero-accent text-[#222222]">smiles</span> with surgical expertise
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl mt-2" style="color: #515151;">
      Rest assured you're in good hands with our exceptional team and state-of-the-art equipment.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-6 justify-around">
      <a href="/about" class="btn-teal inline-flex justify-center items-center px-8 py-2 w-[240px] text-lg">
        Learn More
      </a>
      <a href="/surgery" class="btn-dark inline-flex justify-center items-center px-8 py-2 w-[240px] text-lg">
        Our Services
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-content {
    animation: fadeIn 2s ease-out 0.2s both;
  }
  .hero-heading {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  }
  .hero-accent {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    animation: accentColor 1s ease-out 1.5s both;
  }
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes accentColor {
    from { color: #222222; }
    to { color: #3A959B; }
  }
</style>
